prompts.frontCover: Minimalist cartoon illustration of a single, large piece of nigiri sushi on a white background. The piece of sushi (tuna on rice) is angled as if it's on a snowy slope. A small, charming cartoon figure is dynamically snowboarding down the surface of the tuna, kicking up a spray of rice instead of snow. The style is clean, flat 2D vector art with simple elegant shapes and a limited, soft color palette. In the center, below the illustration, is elegant, handwritten cursive script that reads "Happy Birthday, Jordan". The composition is balanced and whimsical.
